{"tid":1180413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律政司司長鄭若驊竟稱，有關人士可在內地提出申訴","createTime":"2019-05-31T21:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T06:57:11.000Z","uid":41389,"like":372,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"314f2c67b784eb66757f936bd9041c3ef4f89bdd","tid":1180413,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T21:53:52.000Z","msg":"【A1頭條】港府前日就《 逃犯移交 》修訂，提出「小修小補」的新修訂拉攏商界支持，圖盡快通過惡法，有建制派披露，政府擬本月27日表決方案，民主派指政府明顯想避開 7.1 大遊行。民主派昨請政府交代如何協助被「送中」後遭不公平審訊、人權被侵犯的問題，律政司司長鄭若驊竟稱，有關人士可在內地提出申訴，民主派為之咋舌，不滿鄭無視內地冤案受害人申訴無門之苦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1184ae04ee3dbd35eceb6c7469be78f8534aa8","tid":1180413,"uid":103230,"like":258,"dislike":1,"score":257,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T21:57:09.000Z","msg":"律政司實話實說啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港共邊有權同上面申訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇黎得林病一個仲死撐"},{"pid":"a8a34694e4ce1d3d30b6b2bf72d10079f61c8162","tid":1180413,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T21:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46ab57dce2d349fb232f080b730dbff1e96bfc1","tid":1180413,"uid":52090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T23:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471d8e57c9fa1fc7